    "translation": "gardening cooperative / dacha association",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "register": "neutral",
    "naturalMeaning": "The formal name for the collectively organized settlements of dacha plots handed out to Soviet workers and institutions — most dacha communities are still legally organized this way today.",
