    "gender": "n",
    "cefr": "A2",
    "register": "neutral",
    "naturalMeaning": "A collective word for jarred pickled cucumbers, tomatoes, cabbage and mushrooms — the savory counterpart to sweet варенье, both put up in late summer for winter.",
